      "content": "i get that there are two sides but it feels like a bit of an even split in your answer. like, isn't there a way to tell if one is actually more \"correct\" from a legal standpoint? if we're talking about constitutional law, isn't there a standard for what counts as a \"legitimate\" interpretation vs just making things up as you go?",
